Return all the Block PHPP Data as a Dict of Lists of values.

-> {
    'P': ['Electricity (HP compact unit)', 'Electricity (heat pump)', ...],
    'T': [0.0 (KBTU/FT2), 0.8733713455642654 (KBTU/FT2), ...],
    'X': [0.0 (KBTU/FT2), 2.27076549846709 (KBTU/FT2), ...],
